events.name: 強く儚いものたち自動実行

parameters:
Explorer Armada: Handcuffs and leg irons... Is this what
they call aristocratic taste?

Chronos Thief Gang Leader Gift: 'Sir, we have locked up your
daughters in the prison cells and have assigned guards to
watch over them, so there should be no problem.'

Noble Ect: Our daring escape would make a bard sing with
joy.

Chronos Thief Gang Leader Gift: Well, our victims were quite
something too.

Noble Ect: Well, Armada... I think I've come to a point of
no return.

Noble Ect: In the end, I am just a madman consumed by the
obsession to revive the Varié bloodline, just like my
father.

Explorer Armada: No, you're more than that... Not even a
flicker of emotion when receiving reports of the dead.

Explorer Armada: You've become a monster... Orict, who
dreamed of archaeology together, is already dead, huh.

Noble Orict: That's right, that's right! My father's death
robbed me of my dream of archaeology, and his failure cost
me my honor!

Noble Orict: People have disappeared from the mansion! I
have fallen so low as to join forces with the thief gang!

Noble Orict: Monster, very well. I will become a monster
that devours everything.
Noble Orict: Hey, release Armada from her restraints.

Chronos Thief Gang Leader Gift: Master, is it not yet time
to release these people?

Noble Orict: There's been a change of plans... Listen to
what I say without question.
Chronos Thief Gang Leader Gift: Haa, understood.
Noble Orict: Armada, take off your clothes.

Explorer Armada: Are you sane? You're not that kind of
person--

Noble Orict: Just take off your clothes! Don't forget that
we have hostages!

Explorer Armada: ...I understand, I just have to take off my
clothes, right?

Chronos Thief Gang Leader Gift: I don't know why the boss
suddenly changed his mind, but I'm more accustomed to this
kind of development.
Explorer Armada: ...I'm truly disappointed in you.
Noble Orict: The real disappointment is yet to come...!
Noble Orict: Now, let me enjoy myself.
Do you want to skip the adult scene?

Do you want to retry from the battle? If you choose No, it
will result in a game over.
